                        <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  *********************************     -->
                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote>
                                <p>A man is painted on the interior of the cup, squatting over a
                                    vessel. He is bald on the top of his head with shaggy hair on
                                    the sides and has a short beard. He wears a cloak open that
                                    shows his nude body and large genitals. The figure's feet are on
                                    the painted ground line, which does not align with the
                                    orientation of the cup's handles. There are rings of paint
                                    decorating the otherwise empty field behind the figure. The
                                    exterior also has painted black bands and painted petals at the
                                    rim. The underside of the foot has a brief Greek
                                    inscription.</p>
                            </decoNote>
                        </decoDesc>
